                  <bindingDesc>
                     <decoNote type="binding">
                        Sewn at four stations without supports. Bound in full, tight backed, semi-limp red goatskin <material>leather</material> without a flap (Type III binding per Déroche), without endbands. 
                        Cover decorated with gilt <material>leather</material> onlays with a central mandorla featuring a lily design and detached palmette pendants 
                        (note only the bottom pendant remains on the right cover). Blind tooled margins and cross-cross vertical, horizontal, and diagonal lines through the centres.
                        Thick and thin ruled lines in <material>grayish-white paint</material> 
                        framing the perimeters of the boards, with additional radiating lines in the same paint.
                        <dimensions type="binding" unit="mm">
                           <height>237</height>
                           <width>158</width>
                           <depth>11</depth>
                        </dimensions>
                     </decoNote>
